title: [Kodachii's Armory]
[Kodachii's Outfitting]
description: Smooth white plaster walls rise from a russet oak floor.  Just above a polar bear rug hangs a midnight blue rising phoenix tapestry, and an oak beam ceiling completes the picture.  A Vornavian silk-lined display case and a dovetailed oak table stand side by side in the middle of the room.
